reviewText: I showed this on a bus of 30 college students and this video is so boring and covers very non traditional things no one cares about.
This was a great tour of Chicago by boat.  Gave me ideas of what I will do when I visit next year
I think this is very interesting video material.  This is the best way to tour the windy city. This is really DVD Excellence.
I bought this DVD for my dad for Father's Day.  He enjoyed the tour of mostly, newer more updated buildings.  This video had 2 random pauses near the end.
Gives a great history and beautiful views of Chicago. My mom loved it. Brought back alot of memories for her.
